data.description: Rare natural beauty. This waterfront/bayside home is  captivating with unobstructed SUNSET/BAY views. Tucked away on a secluded point in the prestigious 'Sunshine Estates' community on Plantation Key. Expansive property. Well built CBS home designed to enjoy bay views from essentially every room in the house. 4 Beds 4.1 Baths. Vaulted ceilings finished with wood beams. Refinished custom oak wood floors, corian kitchen countertops, dummy waiter, marble bathrooms/bedrooms, built in shelving and and uniquely designed glass block to reflect the colored sunsets. Large floating wood deck surrounded by lush foliage ; for morning coffee or catered events. Ground level consists of covered parking & ''rec room/maid quarters'' w/cabana bath & kitchen for indoor-outdoor entertaining. Crystal clear water, fishing, lobstering, & water-sports right in your own backyard. Quick ocean access via Tavernier Creek. Centrally located to restaurants, schools, shopping, churches & hospital. This is the home you have been waiting for!
